{"tid":581467,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣深高鐵大停駛】港商受累焗搭和諧號企位照殺 遲2小時回港","createTime":"2018-03-05T11:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T13:39:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfab45efb26e4ce6c38f3a457f5f2e6b7df03ad0","tid":581467,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520244930_2aed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520244930_2aed.jpg&h=e5ed4b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深高鐵今日發生故障，部份列車延誤逾300分鐘（5小時），有原本乘搭港鐵城際直通車的乘客亦受影響，行程延誤最少兩小時。由廣州東站回港的港商黃先生指，下午約3時半在廣州東站準備上直通車時前，忽然見到有通知指直通車暫停行駛，無論是3點、4點、5點的班次都沒有車，職員呼籲乘客到另一層的月台，改搭廣深和諧號列車到深圳經羅湖口岸回港。<br />\n<br />\n黃生表示，在廣州東站內並沒接獲通知發生甚麼事，只知道列車暫停，乘客可繼續等候或改搭和諧號，但如決定繼續等候，也沒有確切的恢復時間表。黃生稱，乘客獲告知要轉搭和諧號時大多會都有疑問，班次有何選擇等，但都盡快趕往辦理轉車手續，沒有鼓譟。惟和諧號比較多乘客，最終選擇坐約4時半的車，但只能買到企位，一個半小時全程在餐卡「企足」，沒有直通車的寬敞舒服，而一支510毫升礦泉水賣20元人民幣，黃生又指，直通車職員有告知可以做退票安排，但他因太多人，並沒即時做直通車退票手續，打算回港後再算。<br />\n黃生又指，平時坐直通車只需2小時就能回港，今次要再在羅湖轉東鐵，合共延遲約2小時，而自己明早又要由香港飛上海公幹，曾擔心趕不及回港上機，幸終成功回來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520245821_bd38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520245821_bd38.jpg&h=2fb1f1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520245008_fd89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520245008_fd89.jpg&h=78e51eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180305/57907864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907864&d=EdwsfXnqx%2BIl7aQGhwu2psmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=3d6123e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907864&h=ab0ae0d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180305/57907864</a>"},{"pid":"4bb834bff37d24c3c3f6d7d86c0a26e43dca38f1","tid":581467,"uid":164799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"第一日北上咩 黃生"},{"pid":"e529cb737747146ff87fd3c5bd5dfa4146f5723c","tid":581467,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"去得支那 唔係遇左會有任何不公平 不合理 不愉快 不可能嘅事發生係自己身上咩"},{"pid":"b6f9bc1bd70789161c92019d1e7687e3e070f879","tid":581467,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去得支那 唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">預</span>咗會有任何不公平 不合理 不愉快 不可能嘅事發生係自己身上咩</blockquote><br />\nSor呀肥絲"},{"pid":"c711c1b4fcb9f0de9f1c156f4a3131af7f00402b","tid":581467,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"無人可憐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207c7b412c987fee1be927437d26de3cedd96391","tid":581467,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"香港高鐵已被牽連，變成大白象"}]}